OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777633372
OL,3,CUK terror threat level raised to
OL,4,C'severe' after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FThe UK terrorism threat level has been
OL,7,Fraised to "severe" in the wake of the
OL,8,FGolders Green stabbings, meaning a
OL,9,Fterror attack is "highly likely".
OL,11,FThe Joint Terrorism Analysis Centre
OL,12,Fannounced the decision on Thursday, a
OL,13,Fday after two Jewish men were stabbed
OL,14,Fin north London and in the wake of
OL,15,Fseveral attacks in Jewish
OL,16,Fneighbourhoods in recent weeks.
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@RO]qD@ROUqD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777633372
OL,3,CUK terror threat level raised to
OL,4,C'severe' after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FThe body, which is based in MI5 but
OL,7,Fmakes independent assessments,
OL,8,Fpreviously set the threat level at
OL,9,F"substantial", meaning an attack was
OL,10,F"likely".
OL,12,FHead of counter terrorism policing,
OL,13,FAssistant Commissioner Laurence
OL,14,FTaylor, said that police will be
OL,15,Freviewing "all events across the
OL,16,Fcountry" as a result.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@MO]rD@AOUrD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777633372
OL,3,CUK terror threat level raised to
OL,4,C'severe' after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FSpeaking outside Scotland Yard, he
OL,7,Fsaid: "As part of our review into the
OL,8,Fchange in the threat level, policing
OL,9,Fwill be reviewing all events across
OL,10,Fthe country.
OL,12,F"My teams will be working with forces
OL,13,Fto ensure that we have appropriate
OL,14,Fprotective security measures in place,
OL,15,Fthat the appropriate mitigations are
OL,16,Fput in place, and we will be engaged
OL,17,Fwith communities who will be affected
OL,18,Fby large events, as well as those
OL,19,Finvolved in the events, so that we can
OL,20,Fkeep them safe as they can be."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777633372
OL,3,CUK terror threat level raised to
OL,4,C'severe' after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FIn a statement confirming the
OL,7,Fdecision, Taylor said: "The UK has
OL,8,Fbeen experiencing a gradual increase
OL,9,Fin terrorist threats for some time,
OL,10,Fdriven by a rise in both Islamist and
OL,11,FExtreme Right-Wing terrorism.
OL,13,F"Our casework is increasing across a
OL,14,Fnumber of ideologies and within that
OL,15,Fwe are seeing an elevated threat to
OL,16,FJewish and Israeli individuals and
OL,17,Finstitutions in the UK.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777633372
OL,3,CUK terror threat level raised to
OL,4,C'severe' after Golders Green attack
OL,6,F"We are also working against an
OL,7,Funpredictable global situation that
OL,8,Fhas consequences closer to home,
OL,9,Fincluding physical threats by state-
OL,10,Flinked actors.
OL,12,F"Following yesterday's horrific
OL,13,Fterrorist attack, and incidents
OL,14,Ftargeting the Jewish community across
OL,15,Fthe country, there is already an
OL,16,Fenhanced police response in place, and
OL,17,Fall police forces will be reviewing
OL,18,Fthis in light of the change in threat
OL,19,Flevel. "
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
