PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777633372
OL,3,CUK terror threat level raised to
OL,4,C'severe' after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FIt comes as police confirmed the
OL,7,Fsuspect in Wednesday's attack had
OL,8,Fpreviously been reported to Prevent,
OL,9,Fthe Government's anti-extremism
OL,10,Fprogramme, and Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,11,FStarmer was heckled during a visit to
OL,12,Fthe scene on Thursday.
OL,14,FThe 45-year-old British national was
OL,15,Fborn in Somalia and came to the UK
OL,16,Flegally as a child in the 1990s, Home
OL,17,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood has said.
OL,19,FITV News understands his name is Essa
OL,20,FSuleiman.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777633372
OL,3,CUK terror threat level raised to
OL,4,C'severe' after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police confirmed the
OL,7,Fsuspect was referred to Prevent in
OL,8,F2020, but the case was closed the same
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FAfter being heckled on the scene of
OL,12,Fthe attack, Starmer addressed the
OL,13,Fnation, urging the public to "open
OL,14,Ftheir eyes to Jewish pain".
OL,16,F"I call on everyone to come together
OL,17,Fand fight antisemitism. I call on
OL,18,Feveryone to fight for the decent,
OL,19,Frespectful, tolerant Britain, that I
OL,20,Fand millions of people love," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777633372
OL,3,CUK terror threat level raised to
OL,4,C'severe' after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FHe added that those attending pro-
OL,7,FPalestine marches who stand alongside
OL,8,Fpeople chanting or displaying placards
OL,9,Freading "globalise the intifada" are
OL,10,Fcalling for "terrorism" against Jews.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,F"If you are marching with people
OL,18,Fwearing pictures of paragliders
OL,19,Fwithout calling it out, you are
OL,20,Fvenerating the murder of Jews," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@qD@IOUqD@`O]rD@MOUrD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777633372
OL,3,CUK terror threat level raised to
OL,4,C'severe' after Golders Green attack
OL,6,F"If you stand alongside people who say
OL,7,Fglobalise the intifada, you are
OL,8,Fcalling for terrorism against Jews.
OL,9,FAnd people who use that phrase should
OL,10,Fbe prosecuted. It is racism. Extreme
OL,11,Fracism."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, the IOPC has confirmed it
OL,14,Fhas received a referral about police
OL,15,Factions during the suspect's arrest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
