PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777633372
OL,3,CUK terror threat level raised to
OL,4,C'severe' after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FAn IOPC spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Freceived a mandatory referral from the
OL,8,FMet this afternoon, which relates to
OL,9,Finjuries reportedly sustained by the
OL,10,Fman who was arrested following
OL,11,Fyesterday's attacks in Golders Green.
OL,13,F"The man was taken to hospital and
OL,14,Fdischarged the same day. We are
OL,15,Fassessing the referral to decide what
OL,16,Ffurther action may be required."
OL,18,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,19,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,20,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,21,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
